Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:20.87,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:27.83,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久很久 我一直将你的后背
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:32.00,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当作我的依靠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:39.13,SongchnOP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来将自己身处的地方
